a. Cay quan he parent-child cua cac tien trinh

Dua vao bang PID/PPID da cho, ta xay dung duoc cay tien trinh nhu sau:

1 (init)
 └─ 86  WindowServer            (UID 88)
     ├─ 281  iTunes             (UID 501)
     ├─ 282  Terminal           (UID 501)
     │    └─ 287  login         (UID 0)
     │         └─ 293  -bash    (UID 501)
     │              ├─ 461  firefox-bin   (UID 501)
     │              └─ 751  Aquamacs      (UID 501)
     ├─ 531  Safari             (UID 501)
     └─ 726  Mail               (UID 501)

Giai thich cach doc:
- Tien trinh PID=86 (WindowServer) co PPID=1, tuc la con truc tiep cua
  tien trinh init (tien trinh goc cua he thong).
- WindowServer la cha cua 4 tien trinh: iTunes (281), Terminal (282),
  Safari (531) va Mail (726), vi ca 4 deu co PPID=86.
- Terminal (282) la cha cua login (287) vi PPID cua 287 = 282.
- login (287) la cha cua -bash (293) vi PPID cua 293 = 287.
- -bash (293) la cha cua firefox-bin (461) va Aquamacs (751) vi ca hai
  deu co PPID=293.

b. Dung lenh ps de tim tien trinh cha cua mot tien trinh theo PID

Cach 1 - dung tuy chon -o de chi lay cot PPID:
    ps -o ppid= -p <PID>
Vi du tim cha cua tien trinh co PID=293:
    ps -o ppid= -p 293
Ket qua tra ve chinh la PPID, vi du "287". Sau do dung tiep:
    ps -o pid,ppid,comm -p 287
de xem ten va thong tin chi tiet cua tien trinh cha do.

Cach 2 - dung ps ket hop grep:
    ps -ef | grep <PID>
roi doc cot PPID (cot thu 3 trong output cua ps -ef) tuong ung voi dong
co PID can tim.

Cach 3 - xem nhanh toan bo cay tien trinh:
    ps -ejH
hoac
    ps axjf      (tren Linux)
cho phep nhin truc quan cau truc cha-con thong qua thu tu thut le dong.

c. Cai dat va su dung lenh pstree

Cai dat (neu chua co):
- Tren Debian/Ubuntu:      sudo apt-get install psmisc
- Tren CentOS/RHEL/Fedora: sudo yum install psmisc
- Tren macOS (qua Homebrew): brew install pstree

Cach dung pstree de tim tien trinh cha cua mot PID:

1) Hien thi cay tien trinh bat dau tu mot PID cho truoc (xem cac con):
       pstree -p <PID>
   Tuy chon -p in kem PID ben canh ten tien trinh.

2) De tim CHA (va toan bo to tien) cua mot tien trinh theo PID, dung
   tuy chon -s (show parents):
       pstree -s -p <PID>
   Lenh nay se in ra duong di tu tien trinh goc (init/systemd) xuong toi
   tien trinh co PID duoc chi dinh, nho do thay duoc ngay tien trinh cha
   truc tiep (vd: dung -s 293 se cho thay nhanh init -> ... -> bash(293)).

3) Co the ket hop them -u de xem UID, -a de xem tham so dong lenh:
       pstree -s -u -a -p 293


==================================================================
BAI 2: CHUONG TRINH FORK() IN RA KET QUA GI?
==================================================================

Code:
    pid_t pid;
    int num_coconuts = 17;
    pid = fork();
    if (pid == 0) {
        num_coconuts = 42;
        exit(0);
    } else {
        wait(NULL);
    }
    printf("I see %d coconuts!\n", num_coconuts);
    exit(0);

Ket qua in ra: 

    I see 17 coconuts!

va dong nay CHI duoc in MOT LAN DUY NHAT (boi tien trinh cha).

Giai thich:

1) fork() tao ra mot tien trinh con la BAN SAO doc lap cua tien trinh
   cha tai thoi diem goi fork(). Tu thoi diem do, hai tien trinh co hai
   khong gian dia chi (address space) RIENG BIET, hoan toan tach roi
   nhau (co che copy-on-write o muc he dieu hanh nhung ve mat logic
   moi tien trinh co bien rieng). Bien num_coconuts trong tien trinh con
   chi la BAN SAO cua bien num_coconuts trong tien trinh cha.

2) Sau fork():
   - Tien trinh con nhan duoc gia tri tra ve pid == 0, nen vao nhanh
     if: gan num_coconuts = 42 (chi thay doi ban sao CUA RIENG NO), roi
     goi exit(0) NGAY LAP TUC -> tien trinh con KET THUC tai day va
     KHONG BAO GIO chay den cau lenh printf ben duoi. Do do gia tri 42
     khong bao gio duoc in ra.
   - Tien trinh cha nhan duoc gia tri tra ve pid > 0 (la PID cua con),
     nen vao nhanh else: goi wait(NULL) de cho tien trinh con ket thuc
     truoc (tranh tien trinh con tro thanh zombie va dam bao thu tu).
     Sau khi wait() tra ve, tien trinh cha tiep tuc chay xuong cau lenh
     printf, luc nay bien num_coconuts CUA NO van con gia tri 17 (vi
     no khong bi anh huong boi viec con thay doi ban sao cua minh).

3) Vi vay chuong trinh chi in ra dung mot dong "I see 17 coconuts!" do
   tien trinh cha thuc hien, the hien ro rang nguyen ly: sau fork(),
   bo nho (bien) cua hai tien trinh la doc lap, thay doi o tien trinh
   nay khong lam thay doi gia tri tuong ung o tien trinh kia.


==================================================================
BAI 3: CAC HAM PTHREAD_ATTR_ THAY DOI THUOC TINH CUA POSIX THREAD
==================================================================

Truoc khi tao thread bang pthread_create(), ta co the cau hinh cac
thuoc tinh cua thread thong qua mot bien kieu pthread_attr_t. Cac ham
chinh (tat ca bat dau bang pthread_attr_):

1) pthread_attr_init(pthread_attr_t *attr)
   Khoi tao doi tuong attr voi cac gia tri mac dinh cua he thong.
   Phai goi truoc khi dung bat ky ham set/get nao khac.

2) pthread_attr_destroy(pthread_attr_t *attr)
   Giai phong tai nguyen lien quan den attr sau khi da dung xong
   (khong con dung de tao thread nao nua).

3) pthread_attr_setdetachstate() / pthread_attr_getdetachstate()
   Thiet lap/doc trang thai "detach":
   - PTHREAD_CREATE_JOINABLE (mac dinh): thread chinh phai goi
     pthread_join() de thu hoi tai nguyen cua thread con khi no ket
     thuc, neu khong thread con se ton tai duoi dang "zombie thread".
   - PTHREAD_CREATE_DETACHED: thread tu dong giai phong tai nguyen
     khi ket thuc, khong can va khong duoc goi pthread_join().

4) pthread_attr_setschedpolicy() / pthread_attr_getschedpolicy()
   Thiet lap chinh sach lap lich CPU cho thread: SCHED_OTHER (mac
   dinh, chia se thoi gian thong thuong), SCHED_FIFO hoac SCHED_RR
   (thoi gian thuc - realtime), anh huong thu tu/uu tien thread duoc
   CPU cap phat thuc thi.

5) pthread_attr_setschedparam() / pthread_attr_getschedparam()
   Thiet lap tham so lap lich (vd: do uu tien - sched_priority) di
   kem voi chinh sach lap lich da chon o tren.

6) pthread_attr_setinheritsched() / pthread_attr_getinheritsched()
   Quyet dinh thread moi co KE THUA chinh sach/tham so lap lich tu
   thread cha (PTHREAD_INHERIT_SCHED) hay dung gia tri rieng da set
   trong attr (PTHREAD_EXPLICIT_SCHED).

7) pthread_attr_setscope() / pthread_attr_getscope()
   Thiet lap pham vi tranh chap CPU: PTHREAD_SCOPE_SYSTEM (thread
   tranh chap CPU truc tiep voi cac thread khac trong toan he thong)
   hoac PTHREAD_SCOPE_PROCESS (tranh chap trong noi bo tien trinh).

8) pthread_attr_setstacksize() / pthread_attr_getstacksize()
   Thiet lap/doc kich thuoc vung nho stack danh cho thread (tinh
   bang byte). Huu ich khi thread can stack lon hon (de qui sau) hoac
   muon gioi han bo nho khi tao rat nhieu thread.

9) pthread_attr_setstack() / pthread_attr_getstack()
   Thiet lap/doc dia chi va kich thuoc vung nho ma nguoi dung tu cap
   phat de dung lam stack cho thread (thay vi de he thong tu cap phat).

10) pthread_attr_setguardsize() / pthread_attr_getguardsize()
    Thiet lap/doc kich thuoc vung "guard" (vung bao ve) duoc them vao
    cuoi stack de phat hien tran stack (stack overflow).

Vi du minh hoa: tac dong cua thuoc tinh DETACH STATE
------------------------------------------------------------
/* exercise_3_detach.c - minh hoa pthread_attr_setdetachstate */
#include <stdio.h>
#include <pthread.h>
#include <unistd.h>

void *thread_func(void *arg) {
    printf("Thread con dang chay, sap ket thuc...\n");
    return NULL;
}

int main() {
    pthread_t tid;
    pthread_attr_t attr;

    pthread_attr_init(&attr);                 /* (1) khoi tao attr      */
    pthread_attr_setdetachstate(&attr,
        PTHREAD_CREATE_DETACHED);              /* (2) dat che do detached:
                                                   thread se tu giai phong
                                                   tai nguyen khi ket thuc,
                                                   khong can join          */

    pthread_create(&tid, &attr, thread_func, NULL);
    pthread_attr_destroy(&attr);               /* (3) huy attr, da dung xong */

    /* Vi thread duoc tao o che do DETACHED, neu goi pthread_join(tid,..)
       o day se tra ve loi EINVAL. Thay vao do chuong trinh chinh chi
       can cho du lau de thread con kip in thong bao roi ket thuc.    */
    sleep(1);
    printf("Main ket thuc.\n");
    return 0;
}
------------------------------------------------------------
Giai thich: neu dat PTHREAD_CREATE_JOINABLE (mac dinh) ma main() ket
thuc (hoac thoat) ma khong goi pthread_join(), tai nguyen cua thread se
khong duoc thu hoi dung cach. Nguoc lai, voi PTHREAD_CREATE_DETACHED,
he dieu hanh tu dong don tai nguyen cua thread ngay khi thread ket
thuc, giup don gian hoa quan ly trong cac truong hop khong can lay ket
qua tra ve cua thread (khong can pthread_join).


